    "Preheat the oven to 160\u00b0C/gas mark 3. Place the\nduck legs in a heavy-based ovenproof pan in which\nthey fit snugly and scatter over the garlic and 11/2 tsp\nsea salt. Add the muslin bag of herbs and spices.",
