    "Meanwhile, for the dressing, put the red onion,\ncider vinegar and 2 tbsp water into a small pan\nand simmer for 2-3 minutes or until the liquid has\nreduced by half. Remove from the heat and whisk 1n\nthe mustard and rapeseed oil. Season with salt and\npepper and set aside.",
