    "Trim the blanched sweetbreads of any fat and\nmembrane, then season them. Melt half the butter\nin a frying pan and cook the sweetbreads, st1rnng\nfrequently, over a fairly high heat for 4-5 m\u00b7nutes\nuntil golden. Drain on kitchen paper and keep warr'1",
