    "Preheat the oven to 150 C/gas mark 2 For the\nbarbecue sauce, simply mix all the ingredients\ntogether in a bowl, seasoning with salt and pepper\nto taste.",
    "Heat 1 tbsp oil in a large, heavy-based frying pan\nover a medium-high heat. When hot, fry the ribs",
