    "Tip the beans into a blender or food processor and\nblend to a puree as coarse or smooth as you like;\nyou may need to add a little water.",
    "For the peas, bnng a pan of salted water to ttie boil\nwith the sugar and mint stalks added Tip in the peas\nand simmer for 4-5 minutes or until tender, then\ndrain and discard the mint stalks.",
